# Gemini CLI hooks are confirmed and wired. See gemini-settings.snippet.json for
# the settings.json content, or just run: scripts/install-gemini-hooks.sh
#
# Mapping (Gemini native events): BeforeAgent -> RUNNING, AfterAgent -> IDLE,
# SessionEnd -> agentq clear. WAITING_APPROVAL is omitted (no clean approval
# event; the watcher is the backstop). Gemini hooks pass input as stdin JSON,
# so --type tags the agent kind.
